        <mxCell id="agent_list" value="• Microsoft Foundry Agent&#xa;• Foundry Models (ChatCompletion / Responses)&#xa;• Foundry Anthropic (Claude via Foundry)&#xa;• Azure OpenAI (ChatCompletion / Responses)&#xa;• OpenAI (ChatCompletion / Responses)&#xa;• Anthropic (Direct Claude)&#xa;• A2A Agent (Remote Proxy)&#xa;• GitHub Copilot Agent&#xa;• Copilot Studio Agent&#xa;• Ollama (Local LLM)&#xa;• Bedrock (AWS)&#xa;• Gemini (Google)&#xa;• Custom AIAgent (Base Class)" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;fontColor=#333333;spacingLeft=5;" vertex="1" parent="1">
