        <mxCell id="tools_list" value="• Function Tools - Custom code agents can call&#xa;• Tool Approval - Human-in-the-loop approval&#xa;• Code Interpreter - Sandboxed code execution&#xa;• File Search - Search through uploaded files&#xa;• Web Search - Search the web for information&#xa;• Hosted MCP Tools - Microsoft Foundry hosted&#xa;• Local MCP Tools - Custom MCP servers" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;fontColor=#333333;spacingLeft=5;" vertex="1" parent="1">
