        <mxCell id="orch_list" value="Built-in Patterns:&#xa;• Sequential - One agent after another&#xa;• Concurrent - Parallel agent execution&#xa;• Hand-off - Transfer between agents&#xa;• Magentic - Dynamic orchestration&#xa;&#xa;Workflow Capabilities:&#xa;• Time-travel - Replay/debug flows&#xa;• Parallel Processing&#xa;• Dynamic Execution Paths&#xa;• Agent Coordination&#xa;• State Synchronization" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;fontColor=#333333;spacingLeft=5;" vertex="1" parent="1">
